media:group.media:description:
The motor I used as a generator was a Guangdong Welling Motor Manufacturing product - a resin pack brushless dc motor rated at 280V 20W model number WZDK20-38G(ZKFP-208-6)

Don't forget to check out Luke's channel found here https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1E8OmOG17VckoPviOPmkMw
